呀，厲害了我的國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後都唔會對現任正苦有任何幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，總之佢哋一日要管住我哋，一日就冇可能有民生政策。都唔好ff遲啲立法會過半可以制衡正苦，靠販民？守閪呀，票又唔撚去投，popo加薪又照贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。冇可能又好似以前咁守四年，繼我話佢哋入到局應該淨係投反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇吓正苦為咗DQ議員可以有幾粗暴囉，DQ得幾多個啊屌。如果解散埋議會最撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，橫掂我都就嚟冇工開，慢慢同佢哋玩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母今年邊個夠膽攬炒我就投邊個。唔係我就投白票算鳩數</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母HA同正苦蛇鼠一鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"醫護手足可以移民美國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a59206ba53756aa3d5311237c6734491ca36704","tid":1961160,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad044340426e2753769bd40c82e6f8c1c66c039f","tid":1961160,"uid":166817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c25c656cbd0c84d216b060d10f65b00684afc26","tid":1961160,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80713e4f7d81943b40d203fe01a995174185b0f1","tid":1961160,"uid":21715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"我罷工之後日日都比膠層針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />調撚曬啲閪更閪位比我做，心諗膠層真係冇嘢做㗎喎，淨係識搞小動作。齊心打武漢肺炎？打你老母咩，話知你死，總之搞事就唔得。仲要下個月續約，睇黎都係等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗番起都覺得自己on9，唔係講罷工嘅決定，係點撚解我以為罷完工政府就會封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />