 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e215b9bbe125bc4a1fd26dc7bb4bbbb4eecfb028","tid":1961160,"uid":2084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:37:48.000Z","msg":"HA係大仆街唔係今日嘅事<br />\n轉咗藥都唔同醫生講㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n呢排覆診都感受到你哋情緒，病人其實都受咗好多氣<br />\n因為屋企人lung ca +做完手術會咳，好撚無辜其實，但又唔怪得你哋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其醫生只需要問診的話，應該經視像對話咪算，唔洗冒咁多風險接觸懷疑Case（反正都唔想對多我哋一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"0f39978d6003de454ba2dbfd467825d084ca4392","tid":1961160,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:41:00.000Z","msg":"再罷或者辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2084c73ceb2776613cc2c7c9c07a9b12a6a4fefa","tid":1961160,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:44:40.000Z","msg":"算啦 發完髀氣 聽朝準時返工喇"},{"pid":"1c7caade68cbe34e87f414bcf6488cad8e266daf","tid":1961160,"uid":347944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:47:40.000Z","msg":"全部辭職<br />\n你哋絕對可以收政府皮"},{"pid":"fc53c172f605832de069bf37751e25e389b3944a","tid":1961160,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T19:23:47.000Z","msg":"小心白票兵d人入黎屌你呀樓豬<br />\n<br />\n支持醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbadafbbc84ebeb16200086a76b7ebf04fc95cb","tid":1961160,"uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T19:23:51.000Z","msg":"我明呀 都支持你<br />\n但你哋下下用condom嚟講 開頭會麻木 後期直情有啲反感<br />\n情況就好似啲標題「點解無人提xxxxx」「全部同我死入嚟」<br />\n<br />\n你哋有咩事連登實撐你 無人唔理你哋 所以唔使咁講嘢<br />\n希望你哋發洩感受嘅同時注意下用詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}